職能治療團體動力                        


  	This class introduces various groups and programs as tools for occupational therapy intervention. The goal is to help those occupational therapy students refine their critical thinking about the group activities they select and the protocols they design in related settings. Background of knowledge will be reviewed and the student will take group leadership and other group roles with instructor's guidance.

課程教育目標 

A. 培育具有專業知能的職能治療人才B. 培育具有人本關懷的職能治療人才 
課程基本素養與核心能力 

[核心能力]職能治療專業技能
具備職能治療專業技能，以提供個案職能表現之評估、分析與治療的能力。溝通表達及團隊合作之能力
培養適切溝通表達及團隊合作能力，以建立良好的醫病關係及專業團隊互動。 
